{"tid":845804,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【必勝】美國政府收到疑含蓖麻毒素郵件　傳收件人包括特朗普及馬蒂斯","createTime":"2018-10-03T03:04:43.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-03T04:42:33.000Z","uid":24140,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"5ad48b16c7a36e219a6daf03dc8cbad0f430cb9b","tid":845804,"uid":24140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T03:04:43.000Z","msg":"美國國防部五角大樓近日收到最少兩封郵件，懷疑含有可致命的蓖麻毒素。另外一封可疑郵件就寄給總統特朗普。郵件已經交由聯邦調查局作進一步分析。<br />\n<br />\n外電報道，寄給特朗普的郵件並非在白宮截獲，但無披露詳情，白宮亦無作回應。<br />\n<br />\n國防部發言人表示，檢驗中心星期一截獲至少兩封可疑郵件，收件人分別是國防部長馬蒂斯和美國海軍作戰部長理查森，而郵件對於國防部人員並無威脅。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1421084-20181003.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1421084-20181003.htm&d=JZQYb0fUoqidTPqKsRS3Al0Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=a7a1949d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1421084-20181003.htm&h=e565a024\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1421084-20181003.htm</a>"},{"pid":"a985f7bde20bce73008ef8b0304ee042cb52eae6","tid":845804,"uid":40804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T03:10:06.000Z","msg":"Mr. White<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fcb9a478839c598ba827bd02edc9d8e6019b7b30","tid":845804,"uid":188,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T03:11:46.000Z","msg":"邊會係本人收信<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁撚多人過濾完先比佢 到手上係copy版本"},{"pid":"04e640b0c3a1bb9427c7dbc9234dafaae813fcae","tid":845804,"uid":58552,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T03:12:34.000Z","msg":"強國人"},{"pid":"179d4f438c417ed31c52fc9a7a829eadef67d6a4","tid":845804,"uid":71768,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T03:17:34.000Z","msg":"難分真與假<br />\n<br />\n係咁敏感時刻做 假設真係成功毒殺 眾矢之的會係？<br />\n<br />\n但一